{"tid":1085950,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"奇洛李維斯Matrix替身變導演  20年後共向經典致敬","createTime":"2019-03-31T14:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T18:01:47.000Z","uid":160973,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"19a5a42fae77e681d284436e907d3c01e1336232","tid":1085950,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"科幻動作經典《廿二世紀殺人網絡》（The Matrix）93年3月31日於美國上映，電影今年正迎來二十周年；而同樣由主角奇洛李維斯（Keanu Reeves）主演的動作鉅獻《殺神John Wick 3》（John Wick 3: Parabellum）就向經典作品致敬，重現了《廿》片中Keanu的對白「槍，好多槍（&ldquo;Guns. Lots of Guns.&rdquo;）」勾起了影迷們的回憶，瘋傳預告片表示期待Keanu的新作。<br />\n<br />\n原來《殺神》系列的導演查德史達赫斯基（Chad Stahelski），就是Keanu《廿》片中的替身，所以今年亦是兩人合作二十周年。Chad早前接受訪問憶述當年《廿》片的試鏡，笑稱是自己生涯中最長、最艱辛的一次試鏡，因導演華高斯基姊妹（The Wachowski）及知名武術指導袁和平對動作的要求甚高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OABwfL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OABwfL&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP9x9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=9c366767\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OABwfL</a>"},{"pid":"2ce4bf12e5b4c8228ae67105eb3985953fdc0851","tid":1085950,"uid":56725,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T14:25:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccc78e1365dff41861f6aaeccdf97cc06afeb339","tid":1085950,"uid":27616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"好記得係99年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639dfd11cb5fbcba10a0fd9f1c1c9eaac5c31789","tid":1085950,"uid":100016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"樓主係垃圾content farm打手，賤種一隻死全家，祝樓主全家生癌生不如死"}]}